subSubSection.paragraph:
Colour
. The carapace of adult 

C. haematocheir

is usually dark green with the anterior parts and margins yellowish to red (see also 
Miyake, 1983
; 
Minemizu, 2000
; 
Lee, 2008: 134
; 
Liu & Wang, 2010: 58
; 
Toyota & Seki, 2014
).
